<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Shan_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Consonants">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Consonants">Consonants</span></h3>
<p>Shan has 18 consonants. Unlike in <a href="/wiki/Thai_language" title="Thai language">Thai</a> and <a href="/wiki/Lao_language" title="Lao language">Lao</a> there are no voiced plosives [d] and [b].</p>
