<td>a.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>6</td>
<td>emphatic</td>
<td>343 <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">˧˦˧</span></td>
<td>Starting mid level, then slightly rising, with a drop at the end (similar to tones 3 and 5)</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
</table>
