<li><i>Shan for English Speakers</i>. <a href="/w/index.php?title=Irving_I._Glick_%26_Sao_Tern_Moeng&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Irving I. Glick &amp; Sao Tern Moeng (page does not exist)">Irving I. Glick &amp; Sao Tern Moeng</a> (Dunwoody Press, Wheaton, 1991).</li>
