<li><a href="http://alif-shinobi.blogspot.com/2009/05/shan-alphabet.html" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Shan Alphabet</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.worldscriptures.org/pages/shan.html" class="external text" rel="nofollow">The New Testament written in Shan</a></li>
<li><a href="http://scripts.sil.org/cms/scripts/page.php?site_id=nrsi&amp;id=Padauk" class="external text" rel="nofollow">SIL Padauk Font (Shan Unicode)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://sealang.net/shan/dictionary.htm" class="external text" rel="nofollow">SEAlang Library Shan Dictionary</a></li>
</ul>
